                        "description": "Update user's interests. Validates against interest catalog.\n\nInterest Categories & Limits:\n- sports: Max 5 items\n- hobbies: Max 5 items\n- additional: Max 3 items\n- activities: Max 3 items\n- nostalgia: Max 3 items\n\nError codes:\n- INVALID_INTEREST: Interest value not in catalog\n- INTEREST_LIMIT_EXCEEDED: More than max items selected"
                    }
